                    <div class="col-12">
                        <div class="service-content-inner d-flex align-items-center bg-white border border-primary rounded p-4 ps-0">
                            <div class="service-icon p-4">
                                <i class="fa fa-hotel fa-4x text-primary"></i>
                            </div>
                            <div class="service-content">
                                <h5 class="mb-4">Convenient Amenities</h5>
                                <p class="mb-0">
                                    o enhance your cinema experience, we offer a range of convenient amenities. Guests can enjoy gourmet snacks and beverages from our cinema concession stand, featuring a selection of artisanal popcorn, 
                                    specialty chocolates, and premium drinks
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<!-- Cinema Benefits -->
<section>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="section-top-border">
            <div class="mx-auto text-center mb-5" style="max-width: 900px;">
                <h5 class="section-title px-3">Benefits</h5>
                <h1 class="mb-0">Cinema Benefits</h1>
            </div>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="single-defination">
                        <h4 class="mb-20">Entertainment Options</h4>
                        <p>
                            Staying at a hotel with an in-house cinema offers guests a unique and convenient entertainment option that enhances their overall experience.
                            Instead of having to search for local movie theaters or deal with the hassle of transportation, guests can enjoy the latest films right within the comfort of their accommodation
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="single-defination">
                        <h4 class="mb-20">Viewing Experience</h4>
                        <p>
                            The hotel cinema also provides an intimate and exclusive viewing experience. Unlike crowded public theaters, hotel cinemas typically offer a
                            more private setting with fewer seats, creating a cozy and comfortable atmosphere
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="single-defination">
                        <h4 class="mb-20">Shared Memories</h4>
                        <p>
                            Movie nights often bring together individuals and families who share similar interests, fostering a sense of community within the hotel. This can be especially beneficial for solo travelers or those
                            looking to make new friends during their trip
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>


